flow-state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|concentrated|deep_focus|creative_movement|physical_rhythm|social_exchange|Depth that becomes original work|You can stay with demanding work long enough to create something thoughtful and original.|You may keep the work inside your own thinking for too long before testing whether it lands.|Let focus build substance, then use one timely response to check the result.|This result is strongest when serious attention creates a solid base. Creative Movement helps that base become more original. Physical Rhythm gives attention a way to recover when it gets heavy. Social Exchange is the outside check that stops the work becoming too enclosed.|active|flow-state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::concentrated
