flow-state|deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange|balanced|deep_focus|creative_movement|physical_rhythm|social_exchange|Flexible work with a thinking base|You can choose the condition that fits the task while keeping depth available.|You may switch conditions too quickly instead of giving one of them enough time to work.|Start with the condition the task needs, then review before changing course.|Deep Focus appears first here, but not heavily. Some work may need quiet attention, some may need ideas, some may need movement, and some may need a useful conversation. The value is flexibility with enough judgement behind it. The risk is using variety before the work has settled.|active|flow-state::deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm_social_exchange::balanced
